{
  "stem": "19502.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 113.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They decided to get [? themself ?] happy and go lucky, the police, the-- the-- the-- the Ukrainian militia, and they decided they're going to get some men to work.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They-- they-- I was going with my father when a guy, [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Redke, ?] he just died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was there-- grabbed my father and he says, we're taking you to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You'll be in the evening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You'll come home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So my father says, go home and tell mother that I'll be in the evening home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Something a child feels in-- in my heart, I felt that's the last I'll see of my father.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He kissed me and he says go, sweetheart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He didn't say sweetheart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], go home, and tell your mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Tell mother not to worry, I'll be home soon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I'll be home in the evening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "All the truth is coming out now from the Ukrainians what happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They took the people to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we knew they're taking [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That's a place seven kilometer from our town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were building down there the road.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I was-- was now, they said, see this road?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Your father built.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- what they told us, they were afraid because they took the able people, they shouldn't rebel or something, and they took them to build that road.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as they got weak, they killed them off slowly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I-- when they took our father and he didn't come, so people used to come that they saw in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said [NON-ENGLISH] is there, and [NON-ENGLISH] is there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- they named the names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we know they-- they were there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And says that's all they want is food, bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know, we didn't have no food.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
